Package info.ryandorman.simplescheduler.dao

info.ryandorman.simplescheduler.dao is made up of the Data Access Objects that provide a simple API for interacting with the data source.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AppointmentDao
    Allows predictable access to persistent Appointment data.
    ContactDao
    Allows predictable access to persistent Contact data.
    CountryDao
    Allows predictable access to persistent Country data.
    CustomerDao
    Allows predictable access to persistent Customer data.
    FirstLevelDivisionDao
    Allows predictable access to persistent FirstLevelDivision data.
    UserDao
    Allows predictable access to persistent User data.
  • Class Summary

    Allows access of persistent Contact data.

    Allows access of persistent Country data.
